text:
🚴Located near the Nature Playgarden West is the Cycling Circuit.
🚴For children who love to cycle, the tri-colour Cycling Circuit is a great way to hone their cycling skills amidst play and fun.
⛑️Please put on the helmet while cycling to protect.
🦺🧑Parents can watch over them by the double swing benches located strategically around the circuilt.
